Frequently Asked Questions

Find answers to common questions about UJET and our services.

When will UJET launch?

We're currently in development and plan to launch our platform in 2024. Join our waitlist to be among the first to experience luxury travel at incredible rates.

How much can I save with empty leg flights?

Empty leg flights typically offer savings of 30-50% compared to standard private jet charter rates, making luxury travel more accessible than ever.

What types of aircraft are available?

Our fleet includes everything from light jets for short trips to ultra-long-range aircraft for intercontinental travel, all from trusted operators.

Is there a membership fee?

Yes, we offer different membership tiers starting from $99/month, each with varying benefits and access levels to our platform.
